{"type":null,"faqId":19352,"title":"华为输入法如何取消输入时的手机振动？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.41527778in;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.110416666in;margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.22222222in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{text-indent:0.29166666in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{text-indent:0.29166666in;margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{margin-bottom:0.2777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p6{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 1  </span><span>在</span><span class=\"s2\">设置</span><span>界面，切换到</span><span class=\"s2\">全部设置</span><span>页签，点击</span><span class=\"s2\">语言和输入法</span><span>。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 2  </span><span>点击</span><span class=\"s2\">华为输入法</span><span>右侧的 </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=64242\" style=\"width:0.22986111in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>，进入华为输入法设置菜单。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 3  </span><span>点击</span><span class=\"s2\">虚拟键盘设置</span><span>。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 4  </span><span>将</span><span class=\"s2\">按下时振动提示</span><span>下方的滑块拖动到最左侧，即可取消输入时的振动。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >图1-1<a name=\"_Toc408418081\"></a>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=64243\" style=\"width:5.0in;height:1.9465277in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span>* 图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span class=\"s2\">----结束</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p6\"></p>\n<br>\n<p class=\"p6\"></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":136,"faqType":"信息与邮件","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2493","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-SMS-Email","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1422608223000,"seriesProductName":"G628-TL00","visitedTimes":13,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}